## 🎯 Checklist

- [ ] Rate limiting tous endpoints publics
- [ ] Timeout tous appels externes
- [ ] Retry avec backoff
- [ ] Validation entrées stricte
- [ ] Circuit breaker services externes
- [ ] Graceful degradation
- [ ] Limite concurrence jobs longs
- [ ] Rate limiting par user
- [ ] Health checks dépendances
- [ ] Backpressure queues
- [ ] Tool call limiting LLM

