## 🔍 Détection

```bash
# Endpoints sans rate limit
grep -r "@router\.(post|put|delete)" --include="*.py" | grep -v "@limiter"

# Appels externes sans timeout
grep -r "requests\.(get|post)" --include="*.py" | grep -v "timeout="

# Pas de retry
grep -r "api_call\|external" --include="*.py" | grep -v "@retry"

# Pas de circuit breaker
! grep -r "circuit.breaker\|CircuitBreaker" --include="*.py"
```

